text: #Finland actually rocks. Finns have mostly figured out: education, healthcare + safety nets; tech; co-existence with Russia; speaking English; etc. They pay debts, invest-invest-invest, survive bleak winters. No wonder some in US don't like comparisons this free Baltic state.
author: BradShannon2

text: Good news for #waleg budget writers today. But new revenue is likely too little to head off tax-increase proposals from majority Democrats. The House plans to release its budget Monday.
